name: Game Boy Advance Song Library
summary: Library of Game Boy Advance (GBA) song files ( .MINIGSF ); stores a list of music from a GBA game that is referenced by the audio program to play the correct music; needs to be located in the same directory as the MINIGSF song files in order to load appropriately.

open.note: Open with an associated app listed below.

windows.display_name: Nullsoft Winamp with Highly Advanced plugin
